description: Tug-E-Nuff Bright Fauxtastic Durable Bungee Tug Toy for Dogs Tug-E-Nuff Dog Gear is a family-run business and a team of agility experts and professional dog trainers that make engaging and exciting toys to get your dogs feeling fired up. It is a super-enriching and super-stimulating way of keeping your pooch happy and active without leaving the house! All Tug-E-Nuff toys are designed for interactive play and should only be used under supervision.
